laughter )

2
00:00:04,570 --> 00:00:06,400
Blue fire: I can’t believe
what i’m hearing.

3
00:00:06,470 --> 00:00:09,300
We’re here to ask
a bunch of criminals for help?

4
00:00:09,370 --> 00:00:11,910
There’s no way
the association approved this!

5
00:00:11,970 --> 00:00:14,280
Sitch: But they have!
We’re in a crisis,

6
00:00:14,340 --> 00:00:16,350
one mankind will never overcome

7
00:00:16,410 --> 00:00:19,050
unless we band together
and unite as one!

8
00:00:19,110 --> 00:00:22,520
Our current heroes,
comprised of 390 class cs,

9
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:27,220
101 class bs, 38 class as,
and the 17 of class s,

10
00:00:27,290 --> 00:00:28,690
are clearly not enough!

11
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:30,990
No one expects you
to work for free.

12
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:32,330
You will be compensated

13
00:00:32,390 --> 00:00:34,530
for every individual monster
you defeat!

14
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:37,230
Heavy tank loincloth:
Compensated?! That’s madness!

15
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:39,640
The association is putting
their faith in this trash

16
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:41,570
to help the world?

17
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:44,410
Criminal: And what
makes you so special?

18
00:00:44,470 --> 00:00:47,110
I’ve killed more people
than you’ve met, Mr. Hero.

19
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,380
Wanna try me?

20
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:49,480
Heavy tank loincloth:
These little wimps...

21
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:51,350
( Criminal groans )

22
00:00:51,410 --> 00:00:53,250
Heavy tank loincloth:
Have no heart at all.

23
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,420
- ( Garou chuckles )
- Sitch: Listen. We have no--

24
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:58,720
garou: Well, now, look at this.
Color me impressed.

25
00:00:58,790 --> 00:01:01,390
She’s good.
Her prophecy’s spot-on.

26
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:03,630
She knew a god-level threat

27
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:06,200
like no one had ever seen
was on its way.

28
00:01:06,260 --> 00:01:08,300
But meathead there’s
got a point.

29
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:10,330
All of these nobodies combined

30
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,070
wouldn’t be enough
to take me down.

31
00:01:12,130 --> 00:01:13,140
Sitch: Huh?

32
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,640
Tell me, who are you?

33
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,370
Garou: The name’s garou.

34
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:18,510
Wrecked a ton
of so-called tough guys,

35
00:01:18,570 --> 00:01:21,410
