will you do if the target

107
00:04:21,690 --> 00:04:23,630
shows the slightest bit
of resistance?

108
00:04:23,690 --> 00:04:25,990
Wild monkey: We will physically
punish him without mercy

109
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:28,000
so he’ll never resist again.

110
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,230
Blizzard: Excellent.

111
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:31,430
Men: Thank you very much,
miss blizzard!

112
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:35,240
Genos: We have moved
up the ranks, master saitama.

113
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:37,210
You are now class b, rank 7,

114
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:39,310
and I am class s, rank 14.

115
00:04:39,370 --> 00:04:40,640
Saitama: All I really did

116
00:04:40,710 --> 00:04:43,280
was just defeat
whatever monsters I bumped into.

117
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:45,050
That’s a big boost.

118
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:48,050
Genos: It is because nowadays
monsters appear almost daily.

119
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,580
You defeat them, but you

120
00:04:49,650 --> 00:04:52,390
do not report those victories
to the association.

121
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:55,260
Since your rank is increasing
despite that fact,

122
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,960
it would appear that multiple
eyewitnesses to those deeds

123
00:04:58,030 --> 00:04:59,490
are reporting your work for you.

124
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:02,500
In other words,
the citizenry is watching you.

125
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:05,400
Your identity as a hero
is becoming well known, master.

126
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:07,240
I believe that,
in a very short time,

127
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:09,270
you might even have
fan clubs pop up.

128
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:11,210
Saitama: What? No way.

129
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:14,210
You don’t even have a fan club,
and you’re class s.

130
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:16,580
Genos: Actually,
I do have a fan club.

131
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:18,950
- ( Game music stops )
- Saitama: Seriously?

132
00:05:19,010 --> 00:05:21,080
( Genos gasps )
High-speed object detected.

133
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:23,280
It is too fast for a human.

134
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:24,290
A monster?

135
00:05:24,350 --> 00:05:26,160
Saitama: Oh, an item.

136
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:29,060
Genos: Master appears
to be preoccupied,

137
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,190
so I will go.

138
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:35,430
This will serve as a chance
to test my new upgrades.

139
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,470
Show yourself.

140
00:05:38,370 --> 00:05:39,470
