141
00:05:39,540 --> 00:05:40,970
What do you want?

142
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,300
Sonic: Where’s saitama?

143
00:05:42,370 --> 00:05:45,410
I obtained information
saying that he lives here.

144
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:47,510
Genos: So are you
a friend of his or something?

145
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:49,480
Sonic: We’ve met
somewhere before.

146
00:05:49,550 --> 00:05:53,580
My name’s speed-o’-sound Sonic.
I’m saitama’s rival,

147
00:05:53,650 --> 00:05:55,550
and i’m here
to settle the score.

148
00:05:55,620 --> 00:05:56,990
Now out of my way.

149
00:05:57,050 --> 00:05:59,120
Genos: Speed-o’-sound Sonic!

150
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:01,520
I recall now.
You are the pervert.

151
00:06:01,590 --> 00:06:04,390
You have the audacity
to call yourself master’s rival?

152
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:05,490
How shameless.

153
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,600
One more step,

154
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:08,100
and you will be eliminated.

155
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,430
( Sonic chuckles )
Quite bold, aren’t you?

156
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:14,370
Okay, then. Just try to stop me.

157
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,070
- ( Game music playing )
- Saitama: There.

158
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:17,340
Wait. Oh, crap.

159
00:06:17,410 --> 00:06:18,940
I overwrote king’s save.

160
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:22,650
After I may have
borrowed this without asking.

161
00:06:22,710 --> 00:06:23,650
Way to go.

162
00:06:23,710 --> 00:06:26,480
He’s gonna be pissed...

163
00:06:26,550 --> 00:06:27,480
Big time.

164
00:06:27,550 --> 00:06:28,650
( Pounding on door )

165
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,450
Huh?

166
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:34,020
Eyelashes: Class b, rank 7,
saitama, step outside!

167
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:36,360
Class b, rank one,
hellish blizzard

168
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:38,160
would like to have
a word with you.

169
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:42,360
Saitama: Uh, i’ve already
got a vacuum cleaner.

170
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:44,230
Eyelashes: What?
We are not salesmen!

171
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:47,140
Each of us
are heroes who outrank you!

172
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:50,240
Blizzard: How do you do,
class-b hero saitama?

173
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:52,610
My hero name
is hellish blizzard.

174
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:54,140
Perhaps you’ve heard of me

175
00:06:54,210 --> 00:06:56,680
saitama: Nope,
not even once. Sorry.

176
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:59,450
Eyelashes: You’re looking
at the class b, rank one hero.

177
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,620
Saitama: Ah, okay, then.
Keep up the good work.

178
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,950
We good?

179
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:07,120
( Wild monkey gasps )
Bastard sure is cocky

180
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:09,120
eyelashes: You don’t seem like
the type who can take a hint,

181
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:10,860
so let me make
this crystal clear.

182
00:07:10,930 --> 00:07:12,490
Every hero
who ascends to class b

183
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:15,930
must first properly introduce
themselves to hellish blizzard.

184
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,370
Saitama: Like, formally?

185
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,870
( Door creaks )

186
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:23,140
Fine. Hello.
My name is saitama.

187
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:25,140
What’s shakin’?

188
00:07:25,210 --> 00:07:27,480
( Blizzard sighs )
I guess that’ll do.

189
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:29,880
Now, then, are you aware

190
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:31,650
of the various factions
in the hero business?

191
00:07:31,710 --> 00:07:33,150
Saitama: Factions?

192
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:35,450
Blizzard: Precisely.
In this industry,

193
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,950
if you aren’t part of a group,
you don’t survive.

194
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,360
Saitama: I don’t get
what you mean.

195
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:41,260
Blizzard: I’m saying
it’s impossible

196
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,890
- to raise your rank alone.
- Saitama: Why?

197
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:45,330
- Blizzard: There are obstacles.
- Saitama: Like what?

198
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,560
Blizzard: Like rivals.

199
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:48,430
Saitama: I’m not
getting this at all,

200
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:50,130
and i’m kinda busy here, so--

201
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,500
blizzard: I’m not done
talking to you!

202
00:07:51,570 --> 00:07:53,000
Saitama: Hmm?

203
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,400
Blizzard: I want you
to join our little group.

204
00:07:55,470 --> 00:07:59,010
If you do, i’ll ensure you
remain in the top of class b.

205
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,280
Saitama: Uh...

206
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:02,010
Huh?

207
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,510
I get it!

208
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:05,180
So what you’re saying is,

209
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:06,950
if I refuse
to align myself with you,

210
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:08,220
you’ll stand in my way!

211
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,920
Do you make threats like this

212
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:13,220
to every new hero in class b,
like a gang leader?

213
00:08:13,290 --> 00:08:16,060
Blizzard: No. I only make offers
to those who catch my eye.

214
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:20,460
Saitama: Are you afraid that I
might take your rank-one spot?

215
00:08:20,530 --> 00:08:22,600
Look, don’t worry about it.

216
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:24,900
I’ll make class a pretty soon.

217
00:08:24,970 --> 00:08:27,500
Speaking of, why haven’t you
moved on to class a?

218
00:08:27,570 --> 00:08:29,240
Blizzard: I’m still waiting
for your answer.

219
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:31,440
Saitama: Obviously
the answer is no.

220
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:34,140
There shouldn’t be a cliquey
pecking order between heroes.

221
00:08:34,210 --> 00:08:35,480
Blizzard:
Time to teach him a lesson!

222
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:36,480
Men: Yes!

223
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:37,880
Blizzard: Rough him up so bad

224
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:39,510
he never works as a hero again!

225
00:08:39,580 --> 00:08:41,050
Wipe that smirk off his face!

226
