( Both roar )

227
00:08:43,050 --> 00:08:44,950
- ( SWAT )
- ( Both scream )

228
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:46,920
( Blizzard gasps )

229
00:08:49,530 --> 00:08:52,260
Saitama: You won’t survive
like that, blizzard.

230
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:54,100
Give it up.

231
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:56,600
Blizzard: What a shame.

232
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:59,540
Guess i’ll
have to handle this myself.

233
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,840
( Saitama gasps )

234
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,510
Is this...

235
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:10,350
Telekinesis?

236
00:09:10,410 --> 00:09:11,980
Blizzard: Yes, exactly.

237
00:09:12,050 --> 00:09:13,350
You don’t seem surprised.

238
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:14,620
Saitama: So are you gonna fight

239
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:17,520
by flinging
rocks and stuff at me? Bad idea.

240
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:21,290
Blizzard: I will make you regret
ever choosing to mock me, fool.

241
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:23,490
I’ll kill you so bad,
you’ll beg for death.

242
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:25,460
Hellstorm!

243
00:09:32,230 --> 00:09:34,600
Flesh peels away.
Bones crack.

244
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:37,970
The brutality of it all
breaks your will in an instant.

245
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,540
You did this to yourself.

246
00:09:39,610 --> 00:09:42,040
You deserve it
for thinking you can surpass me.

247
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:44,310
No one is better than me!

248
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:45,610
All my enemies tremble befor--

249
